                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Where We're Going (Future Focus)</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-lg text-slate-700">
                        <li class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Phase 3-5: Core Therapy (Cognitive Restructuring, Exposure Hierarchy, Avatars)</li>
                        <li class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Cultural Adaptation: Address demo limitations with humanized, multi-lingual voice & regionalized settings.</li>
                        <li class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Therapist Dashboard (Beta) & Full Clinical Pilot.</li>
